WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}OCTOBER 5TH</b></Default>

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:05.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL] Hey, hey, let's go
eat pancakes next time.</b></Default>

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:06.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[girls giggling]</b></Default>

00:00:06.580 --> 00:00:08.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They said it looked
really tasty.</b></Default>

00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:10.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[laughter]
-I totally believe it.</b></Default>

00:00:10.750 --> 00:00:13.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NODOKA] {\i1}Was that{\i0}
{\i1}really Uzuki{\i0}?</b></Default>

00:00:14.250 --> 00:00:17.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}She was gauging my feelings{\i0}
{\i1}as she talked.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:00:17.129 --> 00:00:19.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not like her at all.</b></Default>

00:00:19.129 --> 00:00:21.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hey, Fukuyama.
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:24.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are your thoughts
about Hirokawa today?</b></Default>

00:00:24.539 --> 00:00:26.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think she's pretty cute.</b></Default>

00:00:26.289 --> 00:00:27.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Anything else?</b></Default>

00:00:27.750 --> 00:00:29.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FUKUYAMA]
Uh, she's really cute.</b></Default>

00:00:29.789 --> 00:00:31.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess you're right.</b></Default>

00:00:32.710 --> 00:00:34.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ opening theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:01:40.790 --> 00:01:46.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:02:02.750 --> 00:02:05.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}WHAT FLAVOR IS THE ATMOSPHERE?</b></Default>

00:02:05.750 --> 00:02:07.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}-[MIORI] Oh, Azusagawa!
-Mmm?</b></Default>

00:02:08.039 --> 00:02:09.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yoo-hoo!</b></Default>

00:02:10.169 --> 00:02:12.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] We had second period
English together.</b></Default>

00:02:12.629 --> 00:02:14.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. And when Mai sat
next to me</b></Default>

00:02:14.500 --> 00:02:16.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought my heart
was gonna burst out of my chest.</b></Default>

00:02:16.879 --> 00:02:18.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're overreacting, Miori.</b></Default>

00:02:18.460 --> 00:02:20.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You two seem
to be getting along quite well.</b></Default>

00:02:20.960 --> 00:02:22.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not feeling jealous</b></Default>

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:25.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai's not exactly the best
at making friends</b></Default>

00:02:25.750 --> 00:02:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so it's unexpected.</b></Default>

00:02:27.330 --> 00:02:28.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who isn't?</b></Default>

00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:30.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After we got paired up
during English</b></Default>

00:02:30.750 --> 00:02:32.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we started chatting</b></Default>

00:02:32.789 --> 00:02:35.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And when she mentioned
not having a smartphone</b></Default>

00:02:35.210 --> 00:02:38.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew she was the girl you
told me about the other night.</b></Default>

00:02:38.379 --> 00:02:39.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mmm.</b></Default>

00:02:39.379 --> 00:02:40.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

00:02:40.539 --> 00:02:41.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yum!</b></Default>

00:02:42.289 --> 00:02:44.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, the two of you
really are going out, huh?</b></Default>

00:02:44.960 --> 00:02:47.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm often told we're not
in the same league.</b></Default>

00:02:47.419 --> 00:02:49.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't mean that.</b></Default>

00:02:49.169 --> 00:02:51.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you distance yourself
so naturally.</b></Default>

00:02:51.580 --> 00:02:53.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You guys make a great pair.</b></Default>

00:02:54.460 --> 00:02:56.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you, Miori.</b></Default>

00:02:56.289 --> 00:02:57.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:02:57.330 --> 00:02:59.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:02:59.629 --> 00:03:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't take it.
I just fell in love.</b></Default>

00:03:02.419 --> 00:03:04.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, Mai belongs to me</b></Default>

00:03:04.669 --> 00:03:06.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can't I just borrow her?</b></Default>

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:08.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's enough, you two.
I'm not an object, you know?</b></Default>

00:03:08.750 --> 00:03:10.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh! Hey, at least save me half.</b></Default>

00:03:10.830 --> 00:03:12.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What am I watching right now?</b></Default>

00:03:12.710 --> 00:03:14.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel like I need
to leave or something.</b></Default>

00:03:14.750 --> 00:03:17.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You can stay.
-Yes, please do leave. Uh...</b></Default>

00:03:17.669 --> 00:03:19.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:03:19.379 --> 00:03:20.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:03:20.460 --> 00:03:22.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:03:22.419 --> 00:03:23.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:03:23.460 --> 00:03:26.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Back in high school</b></Default>

00:03:26.250 --> 00:03:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just put on a uniform.</b></Default>

00:03:27.830 --> 00:03:29.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're not
consulting each other</b></Default>

00:03:29.289 --> 00:03:30.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and deciding together, right?</b></Default>

00:03:30.830 --> 00:03:33.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MIORI] Would anyone
do something so cumbersome?</b></Default>

00:03:33.710 --> 00:03:35.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Likely not.</b></Default>

00:03:35.250 --> 00:03:38.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm pretty distressed
about clothes every day, too.</b></Default>

00:03:38.169 --> 00:03:40.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't want people to think
that I'm not cool</b></Default>

00:03:40.879 --> 00:03:42.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I also don't want people
to laugh at me</b></Default>

00:03:42.879 --> 00:03:44.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for being a tryhard.</b></Default>

00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:46.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, I even did a search
for "autumn college outfit"</b></Default>

00:03:46.960 --> 00:03:48.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to pick this out today.</b></Default>

00:03:48.129 --> 00:03:50.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not surprising that people
end up dressing the same.</b></Default>

00:03:51.250 --> 00:03:53.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In high school</b></Default>

00:03:53.419 --> 00:03:55.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>found cute ways to tie neckties</b></Default>

00:03:55.169 --> 00:03:56.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and even swapped our socks.</b></Default>

00:03:57.129 --> 00:03:59.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Back then</b></Default>

00:03:59.210 --> 00:04:00.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>trying to stand out.</b></Default>

00:04:00.710 --> 00:04:03.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Mai.
Where do you buy your clothes?</b></Default>

00:04:04.289 --> 00:04:05.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm... Well, recently</b></Default>

00:04:05.879 --> 00:04:07.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been buying the outfits
I wear during shoots</b></Default>

00:04:07.960 --> 00:04:10.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I like from the stylist
on set that day.</b></Default>

00:04:10.080 --> 00:04:12.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't exactly do that, though.</b></Default>

00:04:12.580 --> 00:04:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But for you to ask
about something so specific</b></Default>

00:04:15.080 --> 00:04:16.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>did something happen?</b></Default>

00:04:16.290 --> 00:04:17.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] What sort of something?</b></Default>

00:04:17.629 --> 00:04:19.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something is something</b></Default>

00:04:19.290 --> 00:04:21.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was just wondering, is all.</b></Default>

00:04:23.379 --> 00:04:26.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] You and Miori
kind of share a similar vibe.</b></Default>

00:04:26.250 --> 00:04:29.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure Mito would hate it
if you told her that.</b></Default>

00:04:29.379 --> 00:04:31.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've got cram school
today, right?</b></Default>

00:04:31.290 --> 00:04:33.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why don't you ask Futaba
what she thinks</b></Default>

00:04:33.170 --> 00:04:34.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about that thing from earlier?</b></Default>

00:04:34.670 --> 00:04:36.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hmm?
-I heard from Nodoka.</b></Default>

00:04:36.750 --> 00:04:38.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That conversation
you were having</b></Default>

00:04:38.750 --> 00:04:40.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was about Hirokawa, right?</b></Default>

00:04:41.709 --> 00:04:43.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:04:45.250 --> 00:04:47.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:04:47.709 --> 00:04:49.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please enjoy your meal.</b></Default>

00:04:49.459 --> 00:04:51.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay. Thanks.</b></Default>

00:04:52.129 --> 00:04:54.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I imagine you're still going
through puberty, Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:57.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm surprisingly very pure.</b></Default>

00:04:57.250 --> 00:05:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Apparently, rascals
are surprisingly sensitive.</b></Default>

00:05:00.379 --> 00:05:03.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on. You do mean
actual rascals, don't you?</b></Default>

00:05:03.540 --> 00:05:05.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa, you appeared
to be rather eager</b></Default>

00:05:05.750 --> 00:05:07.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to tie this incident
to puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:09.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the only thing
that's happened</b></Default>

00:05:09.250 --> 00:05:10.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is an idol who couldn't
read the room</b></Default>

00:05:10.790 --> 00:05:13.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>suddenly gained
the ability to do so.</b></Default>

00:05:13.209 --> 00:05:14.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She never seemed troubled</b></Default>

00:05:14.379 --> 00:05:16.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by her own air-headedness
before, did she?</b></Default>

00:05:16.879 --> 00:05:18.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If not, I really don't see
why she would</b></Default>

00:05:18.959 --> 00:05:21.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>develop puberty syndrome
out of the blue.</b></Default>

00:05:21.290 --> 00:05:23.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I get your point, but...</b></Default>

00:05:23.290 --> 00:05:25.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm thinking it would be okay</b></Default>

00:05:25.079 --> 00:05:26.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if she was simply
reading the room.</b></Default>

00:05:26.879 --> 00:05:28.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But wouldn't it be creepy
if she suddenly</b></Default>

00:05:28.709 --> 00:05:30.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>started matching her clothes
to everyone else too?</b></Default>

00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:32.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Interesting.</b></Default>

00:05:32.500 --> 00:05:34.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Isn't that the exact same
topic you were discussing</b></Default>

00:05:34.959 --> 00:05:37.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with your cute new
female friend earlier today?</b></Default>

00:05:37.250 --> 00:05:39.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Easy now. She's only
a potential friend.</b></Default>

00:05:39.879 --> 00:05:42.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If people are always interacting
with the same information</b></Default>

00:05:42.959 --> 00:05:44.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that information
will then be spread around</b></Default>

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:46.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even without direct contact</b></Default>

00:05:46.540 --> 00:05:49.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and everybody who consumes it
will end up becoming similar.</b></Default>

00:05:49.670 --> 00:05:50.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In some ways</b></Default>

00:05:50.709 --> 00:05:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>isn't that kind of similar
to quantum entanglement?</b></Default>

00:05:53.329 --> 00:05:56.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, with a convenient
interpretation of the results</b></Default>

00:05:56.209 --> 00:05:58.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I believe you could say
they have similarities.</b></Default>

00:05:58.629 --> 00:06:01.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For instance, let's say
there is a community</b></Default>

00:06:01.500 --> 00:06:03.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>experiencing
quantum entanglement.</b></Default>

00:06:03.829 --> 00:06:05.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There is.</b></Default>

00:06:05.290 --> 00:06:07.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, let's say
one of their friends</b></Default>

00:06:07.079 --> 00:06:08.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who is free
of quantum entanglement</b></Default>

00:06:08.750 --> 00:06:09.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>comes and joins them.</b></Default>

00:06:10.040 --> 00:06:11.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, she's joined them.</b></Default>

00:06:11.790 --> 00:06:13.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The girl that came after
would be roped</b></Default>

00:06:13.629 --> 00:06:15.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into the state
of quantum entanglement.</b></Default>

00:06:15.829 --> 00:06:17.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Information will be shared</b></Default>

00:06:17.329 --> 00:06:19.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she will merge
into the community.</b></Default>

00:06:19.500 --> 00:06:21.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't get how
college students can do that</b></Default>

00:06:21.500 --> 00:06:23.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>without discussing beforehand.</b></Default>

00:06:23.329 --> 00:06:26.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm starting to think they have
some unspoken special power.</b></Default>

00:06:26.750 --> 00:06:28.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, if that is the case</b></Default>

00:06:28.290 --> 00:06:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the ones who have developed
puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:06:30.579 --> 00:06:32.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>may not be Uzuki Hirokawa</b></Default>

00:06:32.879 --> 00:06:34.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but perhaps
all the other college students</b></Default>

00:06:34.959 --> 00:06:36.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who are capable
of reading the room.</b></Default>

00:06:36.959 --> 00:06:39.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All of the college students?</b></Default>

00:06:39.290 --> 00:06:40.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As if all college students</b></Default>

00:06:40.579 --> 00:06:42.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are sharing information
subconsciously.</b></Default>

00:06:42.920 --> 00:06:45.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And by doing so</b></Default>

00:06:45.170 --> 00:06:47.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a standardized sense of value
amongst their peers.</b></Default>

00:06:47.750 --> 00:06:50.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's awfully large-scale.</b></Default>

00:06:50.250 --> 00:06:54.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>College doesn't have uniforms
or set classes like high school</b></Default>

00:06:54.209 --> 00:06:56.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which caused people
to become uncertain</b></Default>

00:06:56.129 --> 00:06:58.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and subconsciously create
a consensus that describes</b></Default>

00:06:58.790 --> 00:07:01.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how a college student
should dress and function.</b></Default>

00:07:01.170 --> 00:07:02.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I see.</b></Default>

00:07:02.959 --> 00:07:05.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If that's indeed the true nature
of this puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:07:05.959 --> 00:07:06.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it wouldn't be a surprise</b></Default>

00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:10.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that Uzuki Hirokawa would
get roped into it by the others.</b></Default>

00:07:10.079 --> 00:07:12.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Zukki is Zukki after all.</b></Default>

00:07:12.500 --> 00:07:13.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is an idol</b></Default>

00:07:13.959 --> 00:07:16.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and plastered all over TV
and fashion magazines.</b></Default>

00:07:17.459 --> 00:07:19.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For other ordinary
college students</b></Default>

00:07:19.329 --> 00:07:21.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that are still uncertain
of their identity</b></Default>

00:07:21.629 --> 00:07:23.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she shines so bright</b></Default>

00:07:23.209 --> 00:07:25.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they'd want to avert
their eyes from her.</b></Default>

00:07:25.209 --> 00:07:27.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that would explain
why they swallowed her up</b></Default>

00:07:28.040 --> 00:07:31.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>pulling her into the same
ordinary group as themselves.</b></Default>

00:07:31.290 --> 00:07:32.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:07:32.829 --> 00:07:35.459 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>isn't stuff like this
more in your area of expertise?</b></Default>

00:07:35.540 --> 00:07:37.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Analyzing stuff like that</b></Default>

00:07:37.290 --> 00:07:39.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is what statistical science
is all about, right?</b></Default>

00:07:40.579 --> 00:07:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede?
You guys still not done?</b></Default>

00:07:42.329 --> 00:07:43.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, hey there, big brother.</b></Default>

00:07:43.709 --> 00:07:44.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're heading home.</b></Default>

00:07:44.920 --> 00:07:46.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've gotta take
a look at this.</b></Default>

00:07:46.290 --> 00:07:47.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}MILLION VIEWS 10 HOURS AGO</b></Default>

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:49.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ music plays on phone]</b></Default>

00:08:01.879 --> 00:08:04.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right. Uzuki is totally
going viral.</b></Default>

00:08:05.040 --> 00:08:06.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They just uploaded it today.</b></Default>

00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:09.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But look, the video's
already got a million views.</b></Default>

00:08:10.379 --> 00:08:12.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>OCTOBER 6TH</b></Default>

00:08:12.959 --> 00:08:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>UZUKI HIROKAWA</b></Default>

00:08:18.170 --> 00:08:20.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother, stop staring.</b></Default>

00:08:21.879 --> 00:08:23.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you rather I look
at the real thing?</b></Default>

00:08:25.829 --> 00:08:27.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Actually, that one is better.</b></Default>

00:08:27.750 --> 00:08:29.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. I forbid you
from staring so much.</b></Default>

00:08:30.420 --> 00:08:32.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You seem to be doing
really well lately.</b></Default>

00:08:32.500 --> 00:08:34.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, thanks to everyone.</b></Default>

00:08:34.500 --> 00:08:35.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede was all
worked up yesterday</b></Default>

00:08:36.039 --> 00:08:37.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and showed me the new video.</b></Default>

00:08:37.330 --> 00:08:39.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Apparently</b></Default>

00:08:39.250 --> 00:08:40.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks like it.</b></Default>

00:08:40.629 --> 00:08:42.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My manager
even contacted me this morning</b></Default>

00:08:42.830 --> 00:08:44.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and told me
I needed to be careful</b></Default>

00:08:44.289 --> 00:08:45.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on my way to the campus.</b></Default>

00:08:45.539 --> 00:08:46.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL 1] Hey, it's that girl!</b></Default>

00:08:46.750 --> 00:08:49.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, the one
from the earphone commercial.</b></Default>

00:08:49.210 --> 00:08:51.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's right.
What was her name again?</b></Default>

00:08:51.289 --> 00:08:53.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I think
it was something-Zuki.</b></Default>

00:08:53.500 --> 00:08:54.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's a cutie.</b></Default>

00:08:55.039 --> 00:08:56.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And a good singer, too.</b></Default>

00:08:56.629 --> 00:08:58.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL 2] Wasn't she
on a quiz show?</b></Default>

00:08:58.379 --> 00:08:59.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GIRL 3] Yes, she was!</b></Default>

00:09:00.169 --> 00:09:01.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're quite the influencer.</b></Default>

00:09:02.379 --> 00:09:04.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At this rate, you'll be headed
straight to Koshien.</b></Default>

00:09:04.960 --> 00:09:06.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's baseball, big brother.</b></Default>

00:09:06.789 --> 00:09:08.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, that's right. It's Ryogoku.</b></Default>

00:09:09.039 --> 00:09:11.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Closer. But no</b></Default>

00:09:11.960 --> 00:09:14.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've all been striving
to make it to Budokan.</b></Default>

00:09:14.419 --> 00:09:16.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure you knew that, though.</b></Default>

00:09:16.210 --> 00:09:18.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that Budokan
is a bit closer now?</b></Default>

00:09:18.879 --> 00:09:20.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm. I guess we'll see.</b></Default>

00:09:21.039 --> 00:09:23.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, why is it Budokan?</b></Default>

00:09:23.419 --> 00:09:25.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't really care
where it was</b></Default>

00:09:25.210 --> 00:09:27.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as long as we were aiming
for it together.</b></Default>

00:09:27.830 --> 00:09:30.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I talked with you about this
before, didn't I?</b></Default>

00:09:30.250 --> 00:09:32.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>About how it was really
difficult for me</b></Default>

00:09:32.080 --> 00:09:34.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to make any new friends
after I started middle school.</b></Default>

00:09:34.419 --> 00:09:35.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You did.</b></Default>

00:09:35.460 --> 00:09:37.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every single member
of Sweet Bullet</b></Default>

00:09:37.250 --> 00:09:39.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has their own special place
in my heart.</b></Default>

00:09:39.629 --> 00:09:41.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're way more
than just friends.</b></Default>

00:09:41.919 --> 00:09:44.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's why
I want to perform at Budokan</b></Default>

00:09:44.460 --> 00:09:45.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with everyone together.</b></Default>

00:09:45.789 --> 00:09:46.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For us.</b></Default>

00:09:46.879 --> 00:09:48.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN] Right now</b></Default>

00:09:48.789 --> 00:09:50.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for children
refusing to go to school.</b></Default>

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:53.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But we still lack
the adequate manpower.</b></Default>

00:09:53.580 --> 00:09:56.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you be interested
in being a student volunteer?</b></Default>

00:09:56.419 --> 00:09:58.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The organization
was founded recently</b></Default>

00:09:58.669 --> 00:10:00.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and we're looking for people</b></Default>

00:10:00.210 --> 00:10:02.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who can actively help
with our mission.</b></Default>

00:10:02.539 --> 00:10:04.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right now</b></Default>

00:10:04.419 --> 00:10:06.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for children refusing
to go to school.</b></Default>

00:10:06.460 --> 00:10:08.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Volunteering, huh? How kind.</b></Default>

00:10:08.879 --> 00:10:11.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Virtuous much?
-[laughter]</b></Default>

00:10:13.129 --> 00:10:16.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:10:17.750 --> 00:10:19.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, big brother.</b></Default>

00:10:20.580 --> 00:10:21.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know</b></Default>

00:10:21.830 --> 00:10:24.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>everyone was laughing
at me too.</b></Default>

00:10:25.080 --> 00:10:26.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When they were saying
I was an idol</b></Default>

00:10:26.919 --> 00:10:28.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that couldn't break out</b></Default>

00:10:28.419 --> 00:10:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I wasn't able
to read the room</b></Default>

00:10:30.580 --> 00:10:33.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they were all secretly
laughing at me.</b></Default>

00:10:39.629 --> 00:10:40.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ music plays on speakers]</b></Default>

00:10:41.080 --> 00:10:42.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>OCTOBER 17TH</b></Default>

00:10:42.789 --> 00:10:44.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Zukki, what are you doing?
-[music stops]</b></Default>

00:10:45.419 --> 00:10:48.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's wrong?
You don't have this down at all.</b></Default>

00:10:48.210 --> 00:10:50.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You need to focus more.</b></Default>

00:10:50.330 --> 00:10:51.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry.</b></Default>

00:10:54.250 --> 00:10:55.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:10:55.460 --> 00:10:57.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've got an important
question for you.</b></Default>

00:10:57.539 --> 00:10:59.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, Yamada. What is it?</b></Default>

00:10:59.379 --> 00:11:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, sir, are you close friends
with Uzuki Hirokawa?</b></Default>

00:11:03.080 --> 00:11:06.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs] Chit-chat that has
nothing to do with the lesson</b></Default>

00:11:06.080 --> 00:11:06.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will trouble others.</b></Default>

00:11:07.039 --> 00:11:09.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So let's not do that, okay?</b></Default>

00:11:09.129 --> 00:11:10.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aww!</b></Default>

00:11:10.460 --> 00:11:12.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both groan]</b></Default>

00:11:12.460 --> 00:11:13.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:11:14.330 --> 00:11:15.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}[WOMAN]
{\i1}In the constellation Orio{\i0}n</b></Default>

00:11:16.039 --> 00:11:17.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8\i1}-the super--{\i0}
-[dings]</b></Default>

00:11:17.210 --> 00:11:18.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8\i1}Yes, Zukki.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:18.330 --> 00:11:19.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8\i1}Betelgeuse.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:20.080 --> 00:11:21.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}-[dings]
-[giggles]</b></Default>

00:11:21.289 --> 00:11:23.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Zukki, what's gotten into you?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:23.169 --> 00:11:25.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}That's three correct answers{\i0}
{\i1}in a row.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:25.210 --> 00:11:26.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I guess I'm on a roll lately.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:26.960 --> 00:11:29.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Oh, no. That's pretty terrible{\i0}
{\i1}for this show, you know.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:29.879 --> 00:11:33.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This Uzuki Hirokawa
is truly an interesting girl.</b></Default>

00:11:33.580 --> 00:11:34.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, she sure is.</b></Default>

00:11:34.830 --> 00:11:36.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN] {\i1}...yourself an artist now?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:36.330 --> 00:11:38.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Well, I am in my prime{\i0}
{\i1}after all.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:38.330 --> 00:11:41.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I'm getting a little worried{\i0}
{\i1}about today's ratings.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:41.330 --> 00:11:43.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughter]</b></Default>

00:11:47.379 --> 00:11:48.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Sakuta!
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:11:48.710 --> 00:11:50.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Heading home from work, Koga?</b></Default>

00:11:50.379 --> 00:11:51.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are too, right?</b></Default>

00:11:51.629 --> 00:11:52.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I sure am.</b></Default>

00:11:54.250 --> 00:11:56.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, did something
happen to you?</b></Default>

00:11:56.419 --> 00:11:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something like what?</b></Default>

00:11:57.830 --> 00:11:59.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something is something.</b></Default>

00:11:59.289 --> 00:12:01.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Is that phrase popular lately?
-Hmm.</b></Default>

00:12:01.960 --> 00:12:04.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ street performer singing]</b></Default>

00:12:04.210 --> 00:12:05.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Koga</b></Default>

00:12:05.580 --> 00:12:06.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what are your thoughts
on that guy?</b></Default>

00:12:07.500 --> 00:12:08.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My thoughts?</b></Default>

00:12:09.710 --> 00:12:11.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, what do you want me to say?</b></Default>

00:12:11.500 --> 00:12:13.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just curious what you think.</b></Default>

00:12:14.169 --> 00:12:15.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I think he's amazing.</b></Default>

00:12:16.000 --> 00:12:17.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He has something he wants to do</b></Default>

00:12:17.879 --> 00:12:20.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and has the initiative
to pull it off.</b></Default>

00:12:20.460 --> 00:12:23.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I find that amazing</b></Default>

00:12:23.750 --> 00:12:25.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although</b></Default>

00:12:25.789 --> 00:12:28.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd probably say I've never
heard that song before</b></Default>

00:12:28.580 --> 00:12:29.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and we'd laugh a little.</b></Default>

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:33.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But someday, once that person
becomes rich and famous</b></Default>

00:12:33.210 --> 00:12:34.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I'd brag, like</b></Default>

00:12:34.500 --> 00:12:37.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"I listened to him when he was
a simple street performer."</b></Default>

00:12:38.500 --> 00:12:39.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that a good answer?</b></Default>

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:42.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's absolutely perfect.</b></Default>

00:12:42.129 --> 00:12:46.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, but if we're talking about
celebrities who are close to us</b></Default>

00:12:46.250 --> 00:12:48.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no one comes close
to Sakurajima.</b></Default>

00:12:48.330 --> 00:12:50.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, of course not.
She is my perfect Mai.</b></Default>

00:12:50.789 --> 00:12:52.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh, whatever.</b></Default>

00:12:52.250 --> 00:12:53.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Tomoe!</b></Default>

00:12:53.710 --> 00:12:55.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exclaims] Oh, Himeji.</b></Default>

00:12:55.879 --> 00:12:57.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just finished cram school.</b></Default>

00:12:57.539 --> 00:12:59.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, this is a first-year.</b></Default>

00:12:59.169 --> 00:13:00.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sara Himeji.</b></Default>

00:13:01.879 --> 00:13:02.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello.</b></Default>

00:13:03.379 --> 00:13:06.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-And this would be--
-Mr. Azusagawa, aren't you?</b></Default>

00:13:06.539 --> 00:13:07.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, that's right.</b></Default>

00:13:07.710 --> 00:13:10.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You also go to the cram school
where he teaches, don't you?</b></Default>

00:13:10.289 --> 00:13:13.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I'm not your instructor</b></Default>

00:13:13.379 --> 00:13:16.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not yet, but I am currently
looking for a new math teacher.</b></Default>

00:13:16.960 --> 00:13:19.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, if you want
to properly understand it</b></Default>

00:13:19.129 --> 00:13:20.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd recommend Miss Futaba.</b></Default>

00:13:20.879 --> 00:13:23.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if all you want
is good scores on your tests</b></Default>

00:13:23.129 --> 00:13:24.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm fine too.</b></Default>

00:13:24.169 --> 00:13:26.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mr. Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:13:27.000 --> 00:13:30.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't say interesting.
More like he's just weird.</b></Default>

00:13:30.129 --> 00:13:32.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Koga, can you not get
in the way of my sales pitch?</b></Default>

00:13:32.960 --> 00:13:34.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How on earth
was that a sales pitch?</b></Default>

00:13:36.000 --> 00:13:38.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm so sorry. I didn't mean
to get between you two.</b></Default>

00:13:38.789 --> 00:13:39.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:13:40.289 --> 00:13:43.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, no. No, no, wait!
It's not what you think!</b></Default>

00:13:44.629 --> 00:13:46.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's fine. Don't sweat it, Koga.</b></Default>

00:13:46.500 --> 00:13:49.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm! Make sure you clear up
that misunderstanding</b></Default>

00:13:49.080 --> 00:13:51.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all right, Mr. Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:13:51.419 --> 00:13:53.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}OCTOBER 18TH</b></Default>

00:13:55.789 --> 00:13:56.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:13:58.289 --> 00:14:00.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NODOKA] {\i1}Sakuta, I have a favor{\i0}
{\i1}to ask of you.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:14:01.629 --> 00:14:03.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] If this is about Mai</b></Default>

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:05.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll create a happy
family together.</b></Default>

00:14:05.919 --> 00:14:07.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know that's
not what I'm asking for!</b></Default>

00:14:08.039 --> 00:14:10.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So what then? Is it Zukki?</b></Default>

00:14:10.750 --> 00:14:11.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:14:12.169 --> 00:14:15.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We... had a concert
rehearsal yesterday.</b></Default>

00:14:15.500 --> 00:14:18.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have gigs two days in a row
on Saturday and Sunday, right?</b></Default>

00:14:19.080 --> 00:14:20.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I heard about that from Kaede.</b></Default>

00:14:20.789 --> 00:14:24.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll be at Odaiba on Saturday
and then Hakkeijima on Sunday.</b></Default>

00:14:24.210 --> 00:14:27.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, I'll be on a date
with Mai on Saturday.</b></Default>

00:14:27.210 --> 00:14:28.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh, I didn't even ask you!</b></Default>

00:14:28.710 --> 00:14:31.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaiedey said she's going
to Hakkeijima on Sunday.</b></Default>

00:14:31.629 --> 00:14:34.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would have given her
a guest ticket if she'd told me.</b></Default>

00:14:34.419 --> 00:14:38.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's just being considerate
'cause she's a big fan of Zukki.</b></Default>

00:14:38.250 --> 00:14:40.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know</b></Default>

00:14:42.419 --> 00:14:43.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] So?</b></Default>

00:14:43.419 --> 00:14:45.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The dance instructor
was scolding Uzuki</b></Default>

00:14:45.750 --> 00:14:46.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which is unusual.</b></Default>

00:14:47.000 --> 00:14:48.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I asked her
if she was doing all right</b></Default>

00:14:48.879 --> 00:14:51.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she just shrugged me off
with a fake smile.</b></Default>

00:14:51.289 --> 00:14:54.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Well, that doesn't sound good.
-It's not.</b></Default>

00:14:54.169 --> 00:14:56.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uzuki used to tell me
about everything. [sighs softly]</b></Default>

00:14:57.000 --> 00:14:59.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But these days</b></Default>

00:14:59.830 --> 00:15:02.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And now there are rumors
spreading all over social media</b></Default>

00:15:02.669 --> 00:15:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that Uzuki is graduating
from Sweet Bullet too.</b></Default>

00:15:05.580 --> 00:15:06.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

00:15:07.039 --> 00:15:09.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay. So what's the favor?</b></Default>

00:15:10.580 --> 00:15:13.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If Uzuki is in trouble</b></Default>

00:15:13.539 --> 00:15:15.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't want you
to expect too much.</b></Default>

00:15:16.039 --> 00:15:19.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's probably out of my control</b></Default>

00:15:19.789 --> 00:15:21.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Please do.</b></Default>

00:15:22.039 --> 00:15:23.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[train engine slowing]</b></Default>

00:15:29.129 --> 00:15:30.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mmm?</b></Default>

00:15:30.169 --> 00:15:31.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ suspenseful music playing]</b></Default>

00:15:33.419 --> 00:15:34.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:15:35.629 --> 00:15:36.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NODOKA] Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:15:45.500 --> 00:15:47.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Uh...
-[train engine revving]</b></Default>

00:15:47.629 --> 00:15:50.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:16:06.460 --> 00:16:07.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mmm.</b></Default>

00:16:09.710 --> 00:16:10.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

00:16:12.210 --> 00:16:14.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
Ditching class today, Zukki?</b></Default>

00:16:14.250 --> 00:16:15.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Big brother.</b></Default>

00:16:16.580 --> 00:16:19.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Today... How should I put it?</b></Default>

00:16:19.129 --> 00:16:21.669 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to do
a little self-discovery.</b></Default>

00:16:21.750 --> 00:16:24.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you find it in Misakiguchi?</b></Default>

00:16:24.379 --> 00:16:25.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, I don't know.</b></Default>

00:16:26.580 --> 00:16:28.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's even here, anyway?</b></Default>

00:16:28.500 --> 00:16:31.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think the town's specialty
is tuna.</b></Default>

00:16:34.879 --> 00:16:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ music playing over speakers]</b></Default>

00:16:38.960 --> 00:16:41.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you found the self
that you were looking for?</b></Default>

00:16:42.210 --> 00:16:44.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, it's very tasty</b></Default>

00:16:45.169 --> 00:16:48.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I don't think I found myself
in the tuna bowl.</b></Default>

00:16:49.419 --> 00:16:50.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What should we do now?</b></Default>

00:16:51.919 --> 00:16:53.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go for a ride!</b></Default>

00:16:53.919 --> 00:16:57.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you think self-discovery</b></Default>

00:16:58.289 --> 00:16:59.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think
searching for oneself</b></Default>

00:17:00.039 --> 00:17:02.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is what most people do
on rental cycles, but sure.</b></Default>

00:17:03.080 --> 00:17:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ Uzuki Hirokawa's
"Social World"]</b></Default>

00:17:05.579 --> 00:17:08.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:17:11.130 --> 00:17:13.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder what
all these leaves are.</b></Default>

00:17:13.460 --> 00:17:14.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, those are daikon.</b></Default>

00:17:14.960 --> 00:17:16.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Miura daikon.</b></Default>

00:17:16.289 --> 00:17:17.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're so smart, big brother.</b></Default>

00:17:17.920 --> 00:17:21.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I only know because I came here
for a great school field trip.</b></Default>

00:17:21.579 --> 00:17:22.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, Zukki</b></Default>

00:17:22.829 --> 00:17:24.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where are we passing through
right now?</b></Default>

00:17:24.829 --> 00:17:25.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know.</b></Default>

00:17:26.579 --> 00:17:28.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, where are we heading to?</b></Default>

00:17:28.630 --> 00:17:29.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The sea.</b></Default>

00:17:29.829 --> 00:17:31.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What about a map?</b></Default>

00:17:31.380 --> 00:17:33.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The info desk person said
no distractions</b></Default>

00:17:33.670 --> 00:17:35.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>while driving the bicycles.</b></Default>

00:17:35.460 --> 00:17:37.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, look, it's the ocean!</b></Default>

00:17:37.460 --> 00:17:40.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:17:47.039 --> 00:17:48.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How Nodoka!</b></Default>

00:17:48.380 --> 00:17:50.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, what about Toyohama?</b></Default>

00:17:50.210 --> 00:17:52.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not her. I mean it's tranquil.</b></Default>

00:17:54.170 --> 00:17:56.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-By the way, Zukki...
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:17:56.960 --> 00:18:00.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why did you choose statistical
science as your major?</b></Default>

00:18:00.289 --> 00:18:03.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, big brother, why did you
choose statistical science?</b></Default>

00:18:03.750 --> 00:18:06.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because I thought it would be
the least competitive major.</b></Default>

00:18:06.880 --> 00:18:08.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then the same for me.</b></Default>

00:18:08.789 --> 00:18:10.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's with that?</b></Default>

00:18:10.460 --> 00:18:12.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're not gonna tell me
your true reason</b></Default>

00:18:12.789 --> 00:18:14.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then I am not gonna
tell you mine.</b></Default>

00:18:14.579 --> 00:18:16.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That wasn't exactly a lie.</b></Default>

00:18:16.670 --> 00:18:19.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it wasn't exactly
the truth either, was it?</b></Default>

00:18:19.750 --> 00:18:21.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:18:25.460 --> 00:18:26.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Uzuki grunts]</b></Default>

00:18:28.960 --> 00:18:29.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales sharply]</b></Default>

00:18:30.710 --> 00:18:32.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did Nodoka talk to you
about something?</b></Default>

00:18:34.130 --> 00:18:35.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:18:35.670 --> 00:18:36.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles softly]</b></Default>

00:18:38.500 --> 00:18:39.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother</b></Default>

00:18:39.539 --> 00:18:42.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how old do you think someone
can keep being an idol?</b></Default>

00:18:42.750 --> 00:18:45.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aren't you gonna be
an idol for life?</b></Default>

00:18:45.539 --> 00:18:47.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I used to say stuff like that
in the past.</b></Default>

00:18:48.500 --> 00:18:50.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's different now?</b></Default>

00:18:50.579 --> 00:18:53.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One of my friends from my class
asked me yesterday</b></Default>

00:18:53.750 --> 00:18:56.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Just how long are you going
to keep being an idol?"</b></Default>

00:18:56.920 --> 00:18:59.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that
made you start wondering?</b></Default>

00:18:59.170 --> 00:19:00.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh-uh.</b></Default>

00:19:00.250 --> 00:19:02.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I thought of something else.</b></Default>

00:19:02.829 --> 00:19:03.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's that?</b></Default>

00:19:03.920 --> 00:19:06.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That I didn't want her taking
her frustration out on me</b></Default>

00:19:06.789 --> 00:19:09.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just because she had
a big fight with her boyfriend.</b></Default>

00:19:09.710 --> 00:19:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Isn't that a little harsh?</b></Default>

00:19:11.829 --> 00:19:14.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>People don't usually
put it into words</b></Default>

00:19:14.130 --> 00:19:16.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I'm pretty sure
everyone thinks that way.</b></Default>

00:19:16.539 --> 00:19:17.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales] Yeah, but...</b></Default>

00:19:18.000 --> 00:19:19.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>everyone wants to be something.</b></Default>

00:19:20.039 --> 00:19:21.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is something?</b></Default>

00:19:21.750 --> 00:19:23.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something about yourself
you can be proud of</b></Default>

00:19:23.920 --> 00:19:25.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and say, "This is me."</b></Default>

00:19:25.670 --> 00:19:27.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For you, that something
would be like</b></Default>

00:19:27.210 --> 00:19:29.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you're performing
as a singer or an idol.</b></Default>

00:19:30.380 --> 00:19:31.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But for now</b></Default>

00:19:31.460 --> 00:19:34.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she hasn't been able to find
that something for herself</b></Default>

00:19:34.130 --> 00:19:36.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you shine too brightly
for her eyes.</b></Default>

00:19:37.880 --> 00:19:39.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but still...</b></Default>

00:19:40.039 --> 00:19:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there is kind of a point
to what my friend was saying.</b></Default>

00:19:43.829 --> 00:19:46.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That no one can be
an idol for life.</b></Default>

00:19:47.000 --> 00:19:49.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, maybe Budokan
is out of reach.</b></Default>

00:19:54.380 --> 00:19:55.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Zukki</b></Default>

00:19:55.670 --> 00:19:57.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>lend me your smartphone.</b></Default>

00:19:58.250 --> 00:19:59.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How come?</b></Default>

00:20:01.250 --> 00:20:04.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like Budokan's
closer than you think.</b></Default>

00:20:05.170 --> 00:20:06.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh...</b></Default>

00:20:06.750 --> 00:20:08.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

00:20:16.630 --> 00:20:18.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was farther than I thought.</b></Default>

00:20:18.420 --> 00:20:21.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, we were pretty far
from the train station.</b></Default>

00:20:21.079 --> 00:20:23.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, now that you're here</b></Default>

00:20:23.250 --> 00:20:24.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what do you think of Budokan?</b></Default>

00:20:25.460 --> 00:20:28.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, big brother</b></Default>

00:20:28.289 --> 00:20:31.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how many idol groups
can get on stage here each year?</b></Default>

00:20:31.750 --> 00:20:32.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

00:20:33.250 --> 00:20:34.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Five groups at most.</b></Default>

00:20:35.039 --> 00:20:37.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've been on TV</b></Default>

00:20:37.539 --> 00:20:40.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and more people do stop us
on the streets now.</b></Default>

00:20:40.250 --> 00:20:43.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But so far, we've only been able
to fill venues up</b></Default>

00:20:43.079 --> 00:20:44.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to about 2</b></Default>

00:20:45.000 --> 00:20:47.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How many people do you need
to fill this place up?</b></Default>

00:20:47.579 --> 00:20:48.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>10</b></Default>

00:20:50.039 --> 00:20:53.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, but you knew that
from the beginning, didn't you?</b></Default>

00:20:53.210 --> 00:20:54.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mmm.</b></Default>

00:20:54.250 --> 00:20:57.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew that as soon as I set
this place as our goal.</b></Default>

00:20:57.579 --> 00:20:59.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least I thought.</b></Default>

00:20:59.079 --> 00:21:00.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But now I'm not so sure.</b></Default>

00:21:02.130 --> 00:21:05.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder if this was really
the place I wanted to go to.</b></Default>

00:21:06.289 --> 00:21:09.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't worry about
stuff like this in the past.</b></Default>

00:21:10.500 --> 00:21:11.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then...</b></Default>

00:21:11.420 --> 00:21:13.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was it better for you when
you couldn't read the room?</b></Default>

00:21:14.500 --> 00:21:15.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm-mm.</b></Default>

00:21:15.789 --> 00:21:17.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad I can read
the room now.</b></Default>

00:21:17.880 --> 00:21:20.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll know when your friends
make back-handed compliments.</b></Default>

00:21:20.960 --> 00:21:23.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>True. Kind of like
what you just did.</b></Default>

00:21:24.039 --> 00:21:26.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can understand
stuff like that now.</b></Default>

00:21:26.670 --> 00:21:29.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I can hear everybody's
voices inside my head.</b></Default>

00:21:29.670 --> 00:21:31.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're saying
all sorts of things.</b></Default>

00:21:31.539 --> 00:21:33.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I listen to all of it</b></Default>

00:21:33.579 --> 00:21:36.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I lost sight of what
I truly am in the process.</b></Default>

00:21:37.539 --> 00:21:41.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder if I'm experiencing
puberty syndrome right now.</b></Default>

00:21:41.289 --> 00:21:42.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Probably.</b></Default>

00:21:42.539 --> 00:21:46.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then, if I get better</b></Default>

00:21:46.250 --> 00:21:47.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, probably.</b></Default>

00:21:47.500 --> 00:21:49.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That'd be rough
after going through all this.</b></Default>

00:21:50.750 --> 00:21:53.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother, which version
of myself do you prefer?</b></Default>

00:21:53.670 --> 00:21:55.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think both of them are great.</b></Default>

00:21:55.539 --> 00:21:58.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you don't have a preference?</b></Default>

00:21:58.460 --> 00:22:01.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. That's right.
Both are great.</b></Default>

00:22:02.880 --> 00:22:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think talking to you helped
to clear the fog in my head.</b></Default>

00:22:06.329 --> 00:22:09.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks so much for hanging out
with me all day, big brother.</b></Default>

00:22:11.289 --> 00:22:12.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles softly]</b></Default>

00:22:15.210 --> 00:22:16.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone vibrates]</b></Default>

00:22:16.210 --> 00:22:18.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. Uzuki.</b></Default>

00:22:18.170 --> 00:22:20.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Nodoka? Big brother says{\i0}
{\i1}he has a favor to ask.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:21.000 --> 00:22:22.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Hold on.
What are you saying?</b></Default>

00:22:23.000 --> 00:22:24.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}Toyohama?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:24.170 --> 00:22:26.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Is it too late to still get{\i0}
{\i1}tickets for the Saturday gig?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:27.039 --> 00:22:28.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course not.</b></Default>

00:22:28.250 --> 00:22:29.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I thought
you were going on a date</b></Default>

00:22:29.880 --> 00:22:31.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with big sister on Saturday.</b></Default>

00:22:31.750 --> 00:22:34.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did something happen to Uzuki?
Is she in trouble?</b></Default>

00:22:34.460 --> 00:22:36.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I don't know</b></Default>

00:22:40.130 --> 00:22:42.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:22:43.579 --> 00:22:46.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are no rabbits
on the moon, huh?</b></Default>

00:22:46.289 --> 00:22:47.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no food
or air up there either</b></Default>

00:22:48.039 --> 00:22:49.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so that's probably
a good thing.</b></Default>

00:22:50.420 --> 00:22:52.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not a romantic, are you?</b></Default>

00:22:55.079 --> 00:22:57.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ closing theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:22:58.039 --> 00:23:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF A LOST SINGER</b></Default>

00:23:55.079 --> 00:23:55.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:23:56.039 --> 00:23:58.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NODOKA] {\i1}Oh, Sakuta</b></Default>

00:23:58.130 --> 00:23:59.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NEXT EPISODE
#3 IDOL SONG</b></Default>
